"title": "5885: indifference",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5885",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A neutral attitude to God that is as dangerous as hostility. It is condemned as a rejection of God's love and of the needs of others.</p>\n<h2>Indifference towards God</h2>\n<h3>No desire to seek God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:11\">ROM 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:20\">ISA 42:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:21\">JER 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:6\">ZEP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:15\">MAT 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:12\">MAT 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:27\">ACT 28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:15-Rev3:22\">REV 3:15–3:22</a></p>\n<h3>Refusal to heed God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:2\">JER 37:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:11\">PSA 81:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:10\">JER 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:13\">JER 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:3-Jer25:7\">JER 25:3–25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:15\">JER 35:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:7\">EZK 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:4\">ZEC 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:11-Zech7:13\">ZEC 7:11–7:13</a></p>\n<h3>Refusal to respond to God's discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:3\">JER 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:30\">JER 2:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:27-Jer7:28\">JER 7:27–7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:23\">JER 17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:33\">JER 32:33</a></p>\n<h3>Ignoring God is rebellion against him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:2\">EZK 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:19\">JER 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:26\">JER 7:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:24\">JER 36:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:8\">EZK 20:8</a></p>\n<h3>People ignore God and his warnings at their peril</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:11\">JER 12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:21\">EXO 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:25\">EXO 9:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:10-2Chr33:11\">2CH 33:10–33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:24-Prov1:27\">PRO 1:24–1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:18\">PRO 13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:8\">JER 11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:31\">JER 36:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:5-Jer44:6\">JER 44:5–44:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:5-Matt22:7\">MAT 22:5–22:7</a></p>\n<h3>For those who ignore God's salvation, there is no hope</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3\">HEB 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:24\">JER 7:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:30\">MAT 12:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:23\">LUK 11:23</a></p>\n<h2>Indifference to God's declared intentions</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:30\">EZK 22:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:6-Num32:7\">NUM 32:6–32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:15-Judg5:17\">JDG 5:15–5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:23\">JDG 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:5\">2CH 24:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:11\">PSA 22:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:7\">ISA 64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:10\">JER 48:10</a></p>\n<h2>Indifference of religious leaders condemned</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:2-Ezek34:4\">EZK 34:2–34:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:16-Zech11:17\">ZEC 11:16–11:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:12-John10:13\">JHN 10:12–10:13</a></p>\n<h2>Indifference towards the needs of others</h2>\n<h3>Indifference arises from sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:7\">PRO 29:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:21\">JOB 21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:6\">ISA 32:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:15-Jas2:16\">JAS 2:15–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:6\">JAS 5:1–5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of indifference towards others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:23\">GEN 40:23</a> <em>towards Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:10-1Sam25:11\">1SA 25:10–25:11</a> <em>towards David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:40\">MAT 26:40</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:37\">MRK 14:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:45\">LUK 22:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10\">2TI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:16\">2TI 4:16</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ condemns indifference</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41-Matt25:45\">MAT 25:41–25:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30-Luke10:32\">LUK 10:30–10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19-Luke16:21\">LUK 16:19–16:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's apparent indifference</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:38\">MRK 4:38</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:24-Matt8:25\">MAT 8:24–8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:23-Luke8:24\">LUK 8:23–8:24</a> <em>Jesus Christ sometimes delayed responding to cries for help in order to draw out faith.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:26\">MAT 15:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:27\">MRK 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:40\">LUK 10:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:6\">JHN 11:6</a></p>",
